{"data":{"allProjectsJson":{"sections":[{"button":{"label":"Visit on Github","url":"https://github.com/konstantinmuenster/gatsby-theme-portfolio-minimal","visible":false},"projects":[{"category":"Component Libraries","description":"I led development on Autodesk’s Alloy React component library, building a robust, accessible, and type-safe design system used by more than 30+ feature teams. I created and maintained over 60 core components in React and TypeScript, improved Storybook documentation, and ensured design accuracy and accessibility throughout. My work established a consistent UI foundation for teams across the company that balanced full customization with ease of use.","image":{"alt":"Quick Setup","linkTo":"https://alloy-react-storybook.acc-qa.autodesk.com","src":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"constrained","placeholder":{"fallback":"data:image/png;base64,"},"images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/c7c791973ffad545fe78ab8dfb4f3dcf/2aadf/alloy-react-colors.png","srcSet":"/static/c7c791973ffad545fe78ab8dfb4f3dcf/dd26f/alloy-react-colors.png 100w,\n/static/c7c791973ffad545fe78ab8dfb4f3dcf/113a5/alloy-react-colors.png 200w,\n/static/c7c791973ffad545fe78ab8dfb4f3dcf/2aadf/alloy-react-colors.png 400w,\n/static/c7c791973ffad545fe78ab8dfb4f3dcf/87017/alloy-react-colors.png 800w","sizes":"(min-width: 400px) 400px, 100vw"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/c7c791973ffad545fe78ab8dfb4f3dcf/b59c8/alloy-react-colors.webp 100w,\n/static/c7c791973ffad545fe78ab8dfb4f3dcf/7d71c/alloy-react-colors.webp 200w,\n/static/c7c791973ffad545fe78ab8dfb4f3dcf/a783f/alloy-react-colors.webp 400w,\n/static/c7c791973ffad545fe78ab8dfb4f3dcf/ec02f/alloy-react-colors.webp 800w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"(min-width: 400px) 400px, 100vw"}]},"width":400,"height":313}}},"objectFit":null},"links":[{"type":"github","url":"https://github.com/autodesk"},{"type":"external","url":"https://alloy-react-storybook.acc-qa.autodesk.com"}],"tags":["Typescript","React","CSS","Storybook","Jest"],"title":"Autodesk's Alloy Design System","visible":true},{"category":"Component Libraries","description":"I designed and built the Alloy Table component from the ground up with performance, flexibility, and developer experience in mind. Throughout the process, I gathered developer feedback and conducted internal research to shape a composable API that supports custom cells, column grouping, sorting, selection, sticky headers, responsive layouts, and full accessibility. Now widely adopted across Autodesk, it’s the standard for complex data display in all construction products.","image":{"alt":"Quick Setup","linkTo":"https://alloy-react-storybook.acc-qa.autodesk.com/?path=/story/design-system-table--default","src":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"constrained","placeholder":{"fallback":"data:image/png;base64,"},"images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/8bb52c1b46459c271e8ea4fdc008a385/d8b82/simple-table.png","srcSet":"/static/8bb52c1b46459c271e8ea4fdc008a385/f835e/simple-table.png 100w,\n/static/8bb52c1b46459c271e8ea4fdc008a385/78335/simple-table.png 200w,\n/static/8bb52c1b46459c271e8ea4fdc008a385/d8b82/simple-table.png 400w,\n/static/8bb52c1b46459c271e8ea4fdc008a385/2664c/simple-table.png 800w","sizes":"(min-width: 400px) 400px, 100vw"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/8bb52c1b46459c271e8ea4fdc008a385/4dc58/simple-table.webp 100w,\n/static/8bb52c1b46459c271e8ea4fdc008a385/7a016/simple-table.webp 200w,\n/static/8bb52c1b46459c271e8ea4fdc008a385/4f042/simple-table.webp 400w,\n/static/8bb52c1b46459c271e8ea4fdc008a385/0fbcd/simple-table.webp 800w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"(min-width: 400px) 400px, 100vw"}]},"width":400,"height":325}}},"objectFit":null},"links":[{"type":"github","url":"https://github.com/autodesk"},{"type":"external","url":"https://alloy-react-storybook.acc-qa.autodesk.com/?path=/story/design-system-table--default"}],"tags":["Typescript","React","CSS","Storybook","Jest"],"title":"Alloy Table Component","visible":true},{"category":"UI Implementation"